<div class="p-[10px_40px_20px] rounded-[15px] space-y-4" style="background-color: var(--color-neutral);">
  <h1 class="text-[34px] font-bold" style="color: var(--color-primary);">GLOBAL KOMUNIKA MEMBERSHIP</h1>

  <h2 class="text-[28px] font-bold mt-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">How to Earn Points?</h2>

  <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold mt-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">1. Earning Points from Purchases</h3>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    For every <strong>IDR 1,000</strong> spent on your purchase, you will earn <strong>1 point</strong>. This means that every time you make a purchase, the amount you spend directly translates
    into points that accumulate in your account.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Example:</h3>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[18px]" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    <li>If you spend IDR 10,000 on a purchase, you will earn 10 points.</li>
    <li>If you spend IDR 50,000, you will earn 50 points.</li>
    <li>If you spend IDR 100,000, you will earn 100 points.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    The points are automatically calculated and added to your account, so you don't need to do anything extra after
    making a purchase. The more you spend, the more points you will earn, which will increase your future discount
    opportunities.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold mt-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">2. Earning Points by Folowing Our Instagram</h3>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    As part of the rewards system, you can also earn points by engaging with our brand on social media. Specifically, by
    following our Instagram account
    <a
      href="https://www.instagram.com/global.komunika?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw=="
      target="_blank"
      class="underline"
      style="color: var(--color-secondary);"
    >(@global.komunika)</a>,
    you will receive a <strong>bonus of 150 points</strong>.
  </p>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    This means that once you follow us, you immediately get 150 points added to your account, which is a nice way to
    start earning rewards without even making a purchase!
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold mt-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">3. Earning Points by Reviewing Products</h3>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    We encourage customers to share their experiences with our products. After purchasing any product, you have the
    option to leave a review. By doing so, you will earn an additional <strong>150 points</strong> as a reward
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold" style="color: var(--color-primary);"><strong>Example:</strong></h3>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[18px]" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    <li>You purchase an eSIM and leave a review on our website.</li>
    <li>Once your review is posted, you will earn 150 points for sharing your feedback.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">This helps us improve our products and services while rewarding you for your time and insights.</p>

  <h2 class="text-[28px] font-bold mt-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">How to Redeem Points?</h2>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    Now that you have accumulated points, the next step is to redeem them for discounts on future purchases. Here’s how
    it works:
  </p>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[18px]" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    <li><strong>For every 100 points</strong>, you can redeem a <strong>discount of IDR 2,000</strong> on your next purchase.</li>
    <li>You can redeem points in multiples. This means that if you accumulate more than 100 points, you can redeem them for a larger discount.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold" style="color: var(--color-primary);"><strong>Example of Redeeming Points:</strong></h3>

  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[18px]" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    <li>100 points = IDR 2,000 discount</li>
    <li>200 points = IDR 4,000 discount</li>
    <li>500 points = IDR 10,000 discount</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    So, if you have <strong>500 points</strong>, you can redeem those points for a <strong>discount of IDR 10,000</strong>
    on your next purchase. The more points you collect, the higher the discount you can get!
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-[28px] font-bold mt-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">How Can I Access My Points?</h2>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    Once you’ve signed up for the membership program, you will have a user account on our website. All your points will
    be stored and updated in real-time under your account profile. Here’s how to access them:
  </p>

  {% assign handles = '1,2,3,4,5' | split: ',' %}

  <div class="space-y-6">
    {% for handle in handles %}
      {% assign member = shop.metaobjects.membership[handle] %}
      {% if member %}
        <section class="space-y-3">
          {% if member.text %}
            <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">{{ member.text }}</p>
          {% endif %}

          {% if member.image %}
            <img
              src="{{ member.image | img_url: 'master' }}"
              alt="Membership image"
              class="h-auto max-w-full rounded-[15px] my-2
                {% if forloop.index == 1 or forloop.index == 3 or forloop.index == 4 %}
                  w-1/2 mx-auto
                {% else %}
                  w-full
                {% endif %}"
            >
          {% endif %}
        </section>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed mt-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
    Keeping an eye on your points history helps you manage your balance effectively and plan your redemptions for
    maximum benefits.
  </p>

  <h1 class="text-[34px] font-bold mt-6" style="color: var(--color-primary);">FAQ</h1>

  <div class="space-y-3">
    <p class="text-[18px]" style="color: var(--color-primary);">1. How Can I Earn Points?</p>
    <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
      You can earn points by purchasing, following us on Instagram, and writing reviews. These points can be redeemed for
      discounts on future transactions.
    </p>

    <p class="text-[18px]" style="color: var(--color-primary);">2. How Can I Spend My Points?</p>
    <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
      Each 100 points is equivalent to an IDR 2000 discount. Points can only be redeemed in multiples, so accumulating
      more points allows for greater discounts.
    </p>

    <p class="text-[18px]" style="color: var(--color-primary);">3. How Can I Participate?</p>
    <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-primary);">
      You can simply create an account on our website. Once registered, you can start earning points through various
      activities listed in the first question.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
